OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FFresh to strong west to
OL,6,Fnorthwest winds bringing cloudy skies
OL,7,Fand frequent showers today, which may
OL,8,Fmerge to longer periods of rain during
OL,9,Fthe morning. Best of the limited
OL,10,Fbrightness and lighter winds expected
OL,11,Ftowards Inverness.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRather cloudy evening with
OL,14,Ffurther showers, these focused across
OL,15,Fthe north. Some overnight clear spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping, chiefly towards the
OL,17,Fsouthern end of Great Glen where
OL,18,Fshowers will largely die out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
